description: The fund pursues its investment objective by investing, under normal circumstances, at least 80% of its net assets (plus any borrowings for investment purposes) in equity securities of U.S. real estate-related companies. Such companies may include those in the real estate industry or real estate-related industries. It may also invest up to 15% of its net assets in securities of Canadian issuers. The fund is non-diversified.
name: Janus Henderson U.S. Real Estate ETF
